</p></li><li id="LI_E38C1631665D4BE69728BB4374F0432B" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the top cover. 
</p><note type="important" id="GUID-7215619B-4D8E-42B1-B219-10C1EF6B5FB5" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Do not lean on the strip support. 
</p></note></li></ol></prereq><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_E753369EFDC5426BBE20201BB8995B3D" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_929C0F12811B4096BB70DA320BD9C6C8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">2 Protection caps. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves: 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260 gloves. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-DB340B14-87E5-4FDB-8108-245D16C84FF1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-FFCE62E7-A70E-48C0-A9D8-1343D4E50866" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-F662FF27-B643-4922-8F86-FAD185536D35-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F662FF27-B643-4922-8F86-FAD185536D35-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_7BCF39D178844448B3A21E7E56376710" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to remove</title><table id="TABLE_5FBEFB7447DE4A1D819BDF873A72E3DB" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Squeeze the connector of the optical fiber cable and disconnect the connector. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-18DB8925-37A9-48E1-9328-69C909B2C15D" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-BF688272-3580-4314-A1E7-7EBDF62A9CD2-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-BF688272-3580-4314-A1E7-7EBDF62A9CD2-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><note id="GUID-5FCF9D60-0590-4EA6-9D51-E1C1A9CF4513" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Place 2 end caps on the connector to prevent pollution of the 2 glass fibers. 
</p></note><p class="- topic/p ">Tape the optical cable to the carriage so is does not get stuck or damaged anywhere. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-3B4C3FE9-97E4-4308-B7B2-C0CE42D39A6B" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-4BF0F708-82D4-478C-B53D-A1A25EFAC987-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4BF0F708-82D4-478C-B53D-A1A25EFAC987-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-5D98EF7F-3419-4F59-82AA-FCB2D50C8817" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-F8E4BFD8-7ACD-4FD9-B43E-78BFE5513261-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F8E4BFD8-7ACD-4FD9-B43E-78BFE5513261-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Unlock the module: move the small handle downwards. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-0384CEDC-948F-462C-AA1B-D39F4B59935C" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-C02B99B0-C36D-4E05-A581-D185010A0A0C-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-C02B99B0-C36D-4E05-A581-D185010A0A0C-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Fiber optic transceiver module</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> Fiber </compcodenr></comp>. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-E54A08F2-D6BF-4FEF-8376-5EB0DCDA8B41" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0E7ACDA0-1B16-463C-B656-E8067948E210-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0E7ACDA0-1B16-463C-B656-E8067948E210-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-D85F5E4A-D2C3-4BBF-9476-76D8A578271B" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-F662FF27-B643-4922-8F86-FAD185536D35-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F662FF27-B643-4922-8F86-FAD185536D35-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install</title><table id="GUID-BDB87D50-9E70-4086-AC9E-FA7970C76B0D" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Install in reverse order. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Reconnect the Service jumper, exit SDS and press 'Restart' on the operator panel. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-413D000D-1733-4578-95D7-CBC36AC62908.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Dis-assembly</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
